name: Monster Girls Chronicles - Ileana Quest
description:
Advance by jumping in the lair of the cult of Lilith while finishing off your enemies using your Kunais. Avoid being caught or it will be your end. (Infinity Jumper).

Mini game focused on Ileana the Kunoichi from the main Monster Girls Chonicles game. 

This game is planned to be exported for mobile devices later.
